Note from the Chairman















Comprehensive Wealth Management Today … and Tomorrow
Smithfield Trust can help you with every aspect of wealth management – now and in the future – and ensure that your legacy is passed on seamlessly to your heirs.
We are a privately owned trust company chartered and regulated by the Pennsylvania Department of Banking, but our expertise extends far beyond trust management. In addition to banking professionals, our staff includes investment advisors, attorneys and CPAs, allowing us to provide expert guidance on any issue that impacts your financial well-being.


Services

Trust & Fiduciary
Investment Management
Estate Planning & Administration
Tax Planning
Charitable Planning









