Mark McDonel Biography :


Mark is a certified public accountant and a graduate of DuquesneUniversity. Mark has served as Smithfield Trust Company's chief financial officer from the company's inception. He has several years of financial management experience for closely held businesses including mergers and acquisitions, financings, financial reporting etc. His previous experience also includes seven years at an international accounting firm in both the audit and tax departments. Today�s financial world is becoming increasingly complex. In addition to providing traditional trust services, we at Smithfield Trust Company can offer confidential, independent advice and �second opinions� on various financial matters including tax planning, insurance, financing, business valuation and mergers and acquisitions. We feel this is a value-added service.

 


